fields.description:
*Steps to reproduce the behavior*

{code:js}
(function () {
	'use strict';
	const b = Buffer.alloc(1);
	b[0] = 0;
})();
{code}

*Expected behavior*
The value will be set.

*Actual behavior*
Setting the value fails with the following error message: {{Proxy object's 'set' trap returned falsy value for property '0'}}
